    "causal_summary": "After 003 purged `VOYAGE_API_KEY` from every shell-propagating source and 004 rebuilt the memory vec store under hf-local, three sqlite files at `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/database/` were stale: `context-index__voyage__voyage-4__1024.sqlite` (318MB main + 32K shm + 4MB wal) and the older generic-name `context-index.sqlite` (141MB) from before filename-keying. Disk space aside, the leftover files make \"is Voyage still in use?\" a slower question to answer.",
